# Project Standards

## Code comments language

- All code comments must be written **in English only**.
- Avoid mixing Hebrew and English in the same comment.

```php
// ❌ BAD – comment in Hebrew
// בודק אם המשתמש השלים את הפעילות

// ✅ GOOD – comment in English
// Check if the user has completed the activity
```

```js
// ❌ BAD
// שליחת תזכורת למשתמשים

// ✅ GOOD
// Send reminder to the users
```

## File copyright header

- Every new source file that you create in this project should start with the following header (in a comment appropriate for the language):

```text
Copyright © CentricApp LTD. dev@centricapp.co.il
```

- For example, in PHP:

```php
<?php
// Copyright © CentricApp LTD. dev@centricapp.co.il

defined('MOODLE_INTERNAL') || die();
```

- In JavaScript/TypeScript:

```ts
// Copyright © CentricApp LTD. dev@centricapp.co.il

export function example() {
  // ...
}
```

